        Press and Interviews
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-md text-lg leading-8 text-slate-700">
        Recognitions are like tattoos, you only show them off to people you want
        to impress.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mx-auto mt-14 max-w-lg columns-1 gap-6 space-y-6 sm:mt-16 sm:max-w-2xl sm:columns-2 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:columns-3 xl:gap-8 xl:space-y-8"
    >
